author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Stud cutting tips for Schluter niche…I use a laser and trim square to mark cut locations. The oscillating tool is great for accurate cutting, especially when kitchen cabinets are on the other side. The total height of this opening is roughly 16 inches to account for the niche (13”) and top/bottom plates (3”). Many thanks to @schlutersystems1  for sponsoring this tutorial and making great products 🔥#showerniche #schlutersystems #showerremodel #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
